{{Infobox Figure Skating Competition | title = 1976 Czechoslovak Figure Skating Championships | image = | imagesize = | caption = | comptype = National Championship | startdate = January 03 | enddate =04 | skatingseason = 1975–76 | location = [[Prague]] | host = | venue = | prizemoney = | defendladies = | defenddance = | championmen = [[Miroslav Soska]] | championladies = [[Hana Knapova]] | championpairs = [[Ingrid Spieglova]] / [[Alan Spiegl]] | championdance = [[Eva Pestova]] / [[Jiří Pokorný (figure skater)|Jiří Pokorný]] | previouscomp = [[1975 Czechoslovak Figure Skating Championships]] | nextcomp = [[1977 Czechoslovak Figure Skating Championships]] }}
The '''1976 [[Czechoslovak Figure Skating Championships]]''' was held January 3–04 in [[Prague]]. Medals were awarded in the disciplines of [[single skating|men's singles, ladies' singles]], [[pair skating]], and [[ice dancing]].
