'''Super Dzvezda''' is a children's festival in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]. The first Super Dzvezda festival was held in 1998. The authors of the children's hits include established Macedonian performers, i.e. [[Kaliopi]], [[Jovan Jovanov]] and [[Elvir Mekić]].<ref>[http://www.vecer.com.mk/default.asp?ItemID=1976F058B5BF844280D03013EBB1D403 Vecer]</ref>
