== Partners and sponsors == Videoex is organized by the non-profit association Videoex and supported by private and public funding agencies. Since 2012 the festival is considered a regional institution of the Canton of Zurich and has been incorporated into the cultural mission statement of the City of Zurich. <ref>{{cite web|title=Videoex Friends|periodical=|publisher=|url=http://videoex.ch/videoex/links/|deadurl=|format=|accessdate=2018-04-22|archiveurl=|archivedate=|last=|date=|year=|month=|day=|language=German|pages=|quote=}}</ref>
